<h4>Banquet Introduction</h4>
<p>We cordially invite you to attend the prestigious banquet for the International Conference on Entertainment Computing 2025, to be held in Tokyo.<br />
This year's conference banquet will take place at <strong>Meiji Kinenkan</strong>, a venue of significant historical and cultural importance located within the serene Meiji Jingu Shrine forest:<br />
<a href="https://www.meijikinenkan.gr.jp/english/about/index.html">https://www.meijikinenkan.gr.jp/english/about/index.html</a>.<br />
We would like to provide a gala dinner conducive to both enjoyment and professional engagement, enhancing your overall conference experience.</p>


